dct_description_sm: This feature dataset contains a point data layer representing park features, a polygon data layer representing parking lots, a line data layer representing the park linework, a polygon data layer representing parks, a point data layer representing restrooms, and a line data layer representing trails for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2015. They are feature classes within the geodatabase EauClaireCounty_ParksForest_2015.gdb. The dataset was originally published by the Eau Claire Department of Planning an Development in 2015. The dataset originally was distributed with maps of each park.
